- Regular kernel update
- Tweak s390x configuration to enable new 4.14.x Spectre mitigation options (also enable for 4.16.x)
- Enable USB_STORAGE. I find this handy for a RPI3 to use with a USB stick
- Add a note on how to use the RPI3 with USB storage
- Enable SERIAL_DEV_BUS for `arm64`. This is in the default rpi3 kernel.

